Path: Nushell
Content:
Hofer-Julian did lots of work with long flags/options: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10787] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10777] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10776] 3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10775] 4
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10753] 5
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10752] 6
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10668] 7
p00f 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10780] made hints aware of the current directory
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10778] created a new platform support policy document
, and did lots of version-bump-related work: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10755] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10741] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10726] 3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10725] 4
amtoine did lots of work to deprecate+remove old commands (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10772] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10771] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10718] 3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10716] 4
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10715] 5
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10568] 6
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10567] 7
) and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10687] added 
``toolkit run``
 to run a Nushell revision
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10770] renamed 
``unfold``
 to 
``generate``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10759] updated release-pkg.nu with updated manual instructions
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10738] added coreutils to cp search terms
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10711] added a 
``debug info``
 command to show memory info
jntrnr 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10762] fixed the flag type on release-pkg.nu
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10757] fixed winget release submission error
gaetschwartz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10745] implemented modulo for duration
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10744] refactored the lex_item implementation
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10735] remove duplicate code to simplify 
``lite_parsing``
 logic
Tiggax 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10737] added 
``--ignore-error``
 to reject
0scvr 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10730] allowed empty list inputs in 
``group-by``
 and return empty record
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10727] fixed typos in CONTRIBUTING.md
lavafroth 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10721] escaped path that could be a flag
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10719] fix: only escape path containing numbers if they can be valid floating points
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10709] Extract common logic for setting error in 
``parse_short_flags``
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10720] updated table rendering code to use config color scheme in kv tables and 
``table -e``
bobhy 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10694] allowed filesystem commands to access files with glob metachars in name
